Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從剛才開始一直在查什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天回去的時候我有點事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們可以回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜說的有事是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不明擺著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定是去找白色情人節要送的禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就那麼想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情侶裝什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是被紅緒鼓動的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要一個能用形狀體現和小紅感情的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}事情處理好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們談談好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手帕…雖然顏色不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是跟我的是一對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}配對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佛光！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊咧 白夜你辦完事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出巧克力蛋UMA系列第二彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出新品了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是屈斜路湖的庫希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狂熱的程度又提高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…這個事情對大家要保密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是我不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是被姐姐大人知道了的話就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼被我知道就不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點噁心想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說被我知道了就不得了是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜那是什麼啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼嘛什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…本打算回去的時候給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 姐姐和真白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA系列第二彈、手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真是個好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是被小紅搶先了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣一來要送更加有氣勢的禮物才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要氣餒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟小紅的關係能不能相處好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請做好現在就是關鍵時期的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加油 加油
